Robert Anton Wilson then REALLY gets into 23 alot. As does some bands, like They Might Be Giants.<br>
<br>
So, to use it in Matrix is a joke about jokes about conspiracy theories, made in a movie which is about the unreality of reality, while the movie is a fiction which includes almost all elements of modern conspiracy theory.<br>
